WEBVTT

00:00:00.910 --> 00:00:02.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NOVEMBER 27TH</b></Default>

00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:06.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KOGA] Hey, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:00:06.870 --> 00:00:10.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I came across a Dreaming post
that caught my attention.</b></Default>

00:00:10.080 --> 00:00:13.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah? Is it a dream where Koga
finally finds a boyfriend?</b></Default>

00:00:13.369 --> 00:00:14.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, it's nothing like that!</b></Default>

00:00:14.949 --> 00:00:17.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"I dreamed that I broke
the lights in my classroom</b></Default>

00:00:17.699 --> 00:00:18.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and got hurt.</b></Default>

00:00:18.699 --> 00:00:21.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It happened in class 2-1
of Minegahara High.</b></Default>

00:00:21.329 --> 00:00:24.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So it's when I'm changing
after practice. #Dreaming"</b></Default>

00:00:24.579 --> 00:00:26.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is gonna happen
at our high school.</b></Default>

00:00:26.870 --> 00:00:28.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it's today!</b></Default>

00:00:29.120 --> 00:00:31.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure everything
will be all right.</b></Default>

00:00:31.579 --> 00:00:32.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why?</b></Default>

00:00:32.579 --> 00:00:35.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just leave it to the hero
of justice to save the day.</b></Default>

00:00:36.750 --> 00:00:38.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ opening theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:01:44.659 --> 00:01:50.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:02:06.290 --> 00:02:07.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>FROM BEYOND HILBERT SPACE</b></Default>

00:02:07.700 --> 00:02:08.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks for waiting.</b></Default>

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:10.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry to have you come out.</b></Default>

00:02:10.620 --> 00:02:11.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's okay. I have a shift</b></Default>

00:02:12.080 --> 00:02:14.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>over at the cram school
later today anyway.</b></Default>

00:02:15.500 --> 00:02:16.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>First of all</b></Default>

00:02:16.539 --> 00:02:19.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about the puberty syndrome
Ikumi Akagi is dealing with.</b></Default>

00:02:19.750 --> 00:02:22.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have a feeling the theory
you came up with</b></Default>

00:02:22.120 --> 00:02:23.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>isn't too far off.</b></Default>

00:02:23.409 --> 00:02:25.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I was right, huh?</b></Default>

00:02:25.080 --> 00:02:26.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, and one more thing.</b></Default>

00:02:26.949 --> 00:02:27.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This.</b></Default>

00:02:27.949 --> 00:02:28.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:02:29.250 --> 00:02:31.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIO] Doesn't this have
something to do with you?</b></Default>

00:02:31.870 --> 00:02:33.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NOV 27
MIDDLE SCHOOL ALUMNI MEETING</b></Default>

00:02:33.870 --> 00:02:35.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I'm sure it does.</b></Default>

00:02:35.620 --> 00:02:37.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have my own invitation
right here too.</b></Default>

00:02:38.080 --> 00:02:41.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ikumi Akagi had a dream about
the reunion as well, right?</b></Default>

00:02:42.039 --> 00:02:44.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One where
she injures someone. Yeah.</b></Default>

00:02:44.370 --> 00:02:47.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You seem to have taken measures
about that already</b></Default>

00:02:47.080 --> 00:02:49.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'm not too worried
on that front.</b></Default>

00:02:49.500 --> 00:02:51.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But be careful, just in case.</b></Default>

00:02:51.580 --> 00:02:54.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You might be the one
who ends up getting stabbed.</b></Default>

00:02:54.289 --> 00:02:56.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[footsteps receding]
-Hmm.</b></Default>

00:02:57.539 --> 00:02:59.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SPECIAL INTERVIEW
MAI SAKURAJIMA</b></Default>

00:03:01.250 --> 00:03:04.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Maybe I should stick
a magazine into my waistband.</b></Default>

00:03:20.449 --> 00:03:23.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WOMAN] Oh, you must be
the alumnus that contacted us.</b></Default>

00:03:23.330 --> 00:03:24.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's right.</b></Default>

00:03:24.409 --> 00:03:26.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you sign your name
on the line here, please?</b></Default>

00:03:28.699 --> 00:03:30.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[soft gasp]
-Oh, right.</b></Default>

00:03:31.039 --> 00:03:32.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's another student here</b></Default>

00:03:32.580 --> 00:03:34.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who is writing
a report for college</b></Default>

00:03:34.659 --> 00:03:36.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so you might see her
around the campus.</b></Default>

00:04:05.039 --> 00:04:08.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] So, Akagi, you've been
feeling regret this whole time</b></Default>

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:10.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about how
unknown scars and bruises</b></Default>

00:04:11.039 --> 00:04:13.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>showed up
on my little sister's body</b></Default>

00:04:13.289 --> 00:04:16.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and how I wanted the teacher and
my classmates to believe me.</b></Default>

00:04:17.079 --> 00:04:20.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Those times when all I wanted
was for someone to save me.</b></Default>

00:04:21.079 --> 00:04:22.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BOY] Azusagawa's lost it.</b></Default>

00:04:22.829 --> 00:04:24.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL] I think he's gone insane.</b></Default>

00:04:26.079 --> 00:04:29.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And since that day, you've been
holding on to the regret</b></Default>

00:04:29.160 --> 00:04:30.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that you weren't that person.</b></Default>

00:04:31.699 --> 00:04:33.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That isn't quite right.</b></Default>

00:04:34.660 --> 00:04:36.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What I've been regretting
from that day</b></Default>

00:04:36.790 --> 00:04:38.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was a friend saying</b></Default>

00:04:38.079 --> 00:04:41.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Ikumi, do something to clear up
this tension in the air."</b></Default>

00:04:41.620 --> 00:04:43.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I just
wasn't capable of it.</b></Default>

00:04:43.829 --> 00:04:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Looking back now</b></Default>

00:04:45.370 --> 00:04:47.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>ultimately, I think</i>
<i>I had tripped up then</b></Default>

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:51.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>and was at a complete loss</i>
<i>for what to do to fix things.</i></b></Default>

00:04:52.410 --> 00:04:55.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are these memories what you were
wanting to talk about</b></Default>

00:04:55.290 --> 00:04:56.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after luring me out here</b></Default>

00:04:56.870 --> 00:04:58.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with another fake post?</b></Default>

00:04:59.040 --> 00:05:01.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's good nobody
got injured though, right?</b></Default>

00:05:01.500 --> 00:05:02.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, it is.</b></Default>

00:05:03.000 --> 00:05:05.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But can you make this
the last time?</b></Default>

00:05:05.199 --> 00:05:07.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks to you, I missed out
on going to the reunion.</b></Default>

00:05:07.910 --> 00:05:11.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In a way, we're having
our own reunion here, aren't we?</b></Default>

00:05:11.120 --> 00:05:13.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We are in the classroom
from our memories.</b></Default>

00:05:13.449 --> 00:05:15.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe it's a reunion for you.</b></Default>

00:05:15.449 --> 00:05:17.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it's the same for you
as well.</b></Default>

00:05:18.160 --> 00:05:20.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were commuting
to this classroom, too</b></Default>

00:05:21.199 --> 00:05:24.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>back when you were
in the other possible universe.</b></Default>

00:05:24.329 --> 00:05:25.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ gentle music]</b></Default>

00:05:27.290 --> 00:05:28.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:05:28.329 --> 00:05:30.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This breeze takes me back.</b></Default>

00:05:31.290 --> 00:05:32.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The ocean scent</b></Default>

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:34.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the horizon.</b></Default>

00:05:37.579 --> 00:05:39.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How'd you figure it out?</b></Default>

00:05:39.620 --> 00:05:43.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My suspicions began back
at the matriculation ceremony.</b></Default>

00:05:43.120 --> 00:05:46.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You went out of your way to
spark a conversation with me</b></Default>

00:05:46.160 --> 00:05:48.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and then
I never heard from you again.</b></Default>

00:05:50.120 --> 00:05:52.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though I didn't really
think about that incident</b></Default>

00:05:52.870 --> 00:05:53.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>until recently.</b></Default>

00:05:54.500 --> 00:05:56.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So then, it was after Halloween?</b></Default>

00:05:56.870 --> 00:05:58.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I guess so.</b></Default>

00:05:58.579 --> 00:06:00.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After that</b></Default>

00:06:00.449 --> 00:06:01.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that felt off.</b></Default>

00:06:01.500 --> 00:06:02.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For instance?</b></Default>

00:06:02.699 --> 00:06:05.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like your friendship
with Kamisato.</b></Default>

00:06:05.290 --> 00:06:07.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Saki and I
were in the same class</b></Default>

00:06:07.079 --> 00:06:09.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for our second and third years
of high school</b></Default>

00:06:09.449 --> 00:06:10.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the other world.</b></Default>

00:06:10.620 --> 00:06:13.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then</b></Default>

00:06:13.329 --> 00:06:15.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Those are sensations
from the Akagi</b></Default>

00:06:15.329 --> 00:06:17.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who's in the other world</b></Default>

00:06:18.410 --> 00:06:21.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was the one writing
on your arms, wasn't she?</b></Default>

00:06:23.449 --> 00:06:26.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All you're saying
is speculation, right?</b></Default>

00:06:26.500 --> 00:06:29.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, but I was fully convinced
when I saw my yearbook.</b></Default>

00:06:29.910 --> 00:06:31.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You said that you threw it away.</b></Default>

00:06:31.790 --> 00:06:33.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't you remember, Akagi?</b></Default>

00:06:33.829 --> 00:06:36.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You mentioned that you knew
what I wrote in my yearbook.</b></Default>

00:06:37.250 --> 00:06:39.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Someday</b></Default>

00:06:39.790 --> 00:06:42.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't write
anything like that in there.</b></Default>

00:06:42.699 --> 00:06:46.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That phrase was something
I heard from a certain someone.</b></Default>

00:06:46.500 --> 00:06:49.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hadn't recalled that memory
back in middle school.</b></Default>

00:06:49.699 --> 00:06:52.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why</b></Default>

00:06:53.160 --> 00:06:55.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But me in the other world
could remember those words</b></Default>

00:06:55.870 --> 00:06:57.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>earlier than I did over here.</b></Default>

00:06:57.790 --> 00:07:00.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So he was able to write it
in his graduation essay.</b></Default>

00:07:01.620 --> 00:07:03.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure
he's simply better than I am.</b></Default>

00:07:04.829 --> 00:07:08.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For me, personally, this world
over here is more comfortable.</b></Default>

00:07:09.040 --> 00:07:11.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it because I'm not as good?</b></Default>

00:07:11.160 --> 00:07:12.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh-huh.</b></Default>

00:07:12.790 --> 00:07:15.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you read the essay
I wrote in there?</b></Default>

00:07:15.120 --> 00:07:16.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] "I want to
become an adult</b></Default>

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:18.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that can be of help to others."</b></Default>

00:07:18.750 --> 00:07:20.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] That dream
didn't come true</b></Default>

00:07:20.870 --> 00:07:22.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>over in the other world</b></Default>

00:07:22.410 --> 00:07:25.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because the Azusagawa
over there is good.</b></Default>

00:07:25.449 --> 00:07:26.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Back in middle school</b></Default>

00:07:26.790 --> 00:07:29.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wasn't allowed to do anything
I wanted to do.</b></Default>

00:07:29.829 --> 00:07:32.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even when
his little sister was bullied</b></Default>

00:07:32.120 --> 00:07:34.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa resolved things
on his own.</b></Default>

00:07:34.750 --> 00:07:36.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He took over the broadcast room.</b></Default>

00:07:36.870 --> 00:07:39.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My other self
sure is flashy about things.</b></Default>

00:07:39.579 --> 00:07:41.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was the same
in high school too.</b></Default>

00:07:41.790 --> 00:07:44.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All of the problems
that I wanted to help out with</b></Default>

00:07:44.500 --> 00:07:47.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa was able
to resolve them all by himself.</b></Default>

00:07:48.790 --> 00:07:51.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It wasn't me, but Azusagawa</b></Default>

00:07:51.079 --> 00:07:54.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that became the something
that I wanted to become.</b></Default>

00:07:54.290 --> 00:07:56.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I failed
my college entrance exams.</b></Default>

00:07:56.910 --> 00:08:00.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So on top of that</b></Default>

00:08:02.829 --> 00:08:05.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Not a single thing</i>
<i>worked out for me.</i></b></Default>

00:08:06.699 --> 00:08:09.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>That's why</i>
<i>every day, I would think</b></Default>

00:08:09.120 --> 00:08:12.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>"I want to escape to somewhere</i>
<i>other than here."</i></b></Default>

00:08:12.250 --> 00:08:13.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[singing]</b></Default>

00:08:15.500 --> 00:08:16.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] <i>And then...</i></b></Default>

00:08:21.790 --> 00:08:23.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[soft gasp]</b></Default>

00:08:24.750 --> 00:08:26.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I arrived in this world.</i></b></Default>

00:08:27.699 --> 00:08:29.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>When I came to</b></Default>

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:32.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I was standing at</i>
<i>the tree-lined road on campus.</i></b></Default>

00:08:32.580 --> 00:08:35.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>And that's when I found you</i>
<i>among the crowd.</i></b></Default>

00:08:35.659 --> 00:08:38.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're Azusagawa, right?</b></Default>

00:08:38.120 --> 00:08:39.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm? Oh.</b></Default>

00:08:39.750 --> 00:08:41.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And aren't you Akagi?</b></Default>

00:08:41.620 --> 00:08:44.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought
I was having a strange dream</b></Default>

00:08:44.080 --> 00:08:45.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I wasn't.</b></Default>

00:08:45.750 --> 00:08:47.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I knew right away</b></Default>

00:08:47.289 --> 00:08:49.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because I met you
in the other world.</b></Default>

00:08:51.659 --> 00:08:53.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Back in winter</b></Default>

00:08:53.200 --> 00:08:54.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>during our second year.</b></Default>

00:08:55.659 --> 00:08:56.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:08:56.830 --> 00:08:57.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, yeah?</b></Default>

00:08:58.039 --> 00:08:59.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here. Your turn today.</b></Default>

00:08:59.789 --> 00:09:01.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The bell's gonna ring soon.</b></Default>

00:09:04.500 --> 00:09:06.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm shocked you noticed that.</b></Default>

00:09:07.080 --> 00:09:09.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course I'd notice.</b></Default>

00:09:10.580 --> 00:09:13.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Didn't you ever feel
you wanted to go back?</b></Default>

00:09:13.250 --> 00:09:14.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I haven't.</b></Default>

00:09:14.789 --> 00:09:16.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I still don't.</b></Default>

00:09:16.500 --> 00:09:18.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Over here. I'm a college student</b></Default>

00:09:18.789 --> 00:09:20.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at the school
I wanted to attend.</b></Default>

00:09:20.870 --> 00:09:24.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I represent a volunteer group</b></Default>

00:09:24.080 --> 00:09:25.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A hero of justice.</b></Default>

00:09:26.000 --> 00:09:27.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[soft chuckle]</b></Default>

00:09:27.539 --> 00:09:28.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] <i>In this world</b></Default>

00:09:28.830 --> 00:09:31.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I was able to become</i>
<i>the person I wanted to be.</i></b></Default>

00:09:31.789 --> 00:09:33.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] <i>If that's true</b></Default>

00:09:33.159 --> 00:09:35.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>why'd you challenge me</i>
<i>to that contest?</i></b></Default>

00:09:35.450 --> 00:09:38.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] <i>Because I thought</i>
<i>I would finally have a chance</i></b></Default>

00:09:38.330 --> 00:09:39.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>to win against you.</i></b></Default>

00:09:39.580 --> 00:09:40.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] <i>In that case</b></Default>

00:09:40.950 --> 00:09:42.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>despite having lost</b></Default>

00:09:42.830 --> 00:09:44.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why do you sound so relieved?</b></Default>

00:09:45.539 --> 00:09:46.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] It's because...</b></Default>

00:09:47.580 --> 00:09:48.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Truth is</b></Default>

00:09:48.750 --> 00:09:50.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you wanted someone
to notice, didn't you?</b></Default>

00:09:50.909 --> 00:09:53.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That the Ikumi Akagi
standing right here</b></Default>

00:09:53.080 --> 00:09:54.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>isn't the real one.</b></Default>

00:09:54.700 --> 00:09:57.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why do you think that?</b></Default>

00:09:57.200 --> 00:09:59.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Akagi isn't so easy on herself</b></Default>

00:09:59.080 --> 00:10:01.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that she can forgive herself
for running away.</b></Default>

00:10:02.000 --> 00:10:04.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So it's only logical
that she wanted someone</b></Default>

00:10:04.330 --> 00:10:05.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to catch her cheating.</b></Default>

00:10:05.580 --> 00:10:06.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[soft gasp]</b></Default>

00:10:06.700 --> 00:10:08.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, there you have it.</b></Default>

00:10:09.120 --> 00:10:11.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"I caught you, Akagi</b></Default>

00:10:17.700 --> 00:10:19.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I was a child</b></Default>

00:10:19.580 --> 00:10:21.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I used to be good
at hide and seek.</b></Default>

00:10:22.830 --> 00:10:25.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I always knew</b></Default>

00:10:25.289 --> 00:10:27.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I couldn't
stay this way forever.</b></Default>

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:29.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sobbing] Nobody noticed.</b></Default>

00:10:29.870 --> 00:10:31.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nobody cared to notice.</b></Default>

00:10:32.289 --> 00:10:35.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was losing sight
of my own existence.</b></Default>

00:10:36.200 --> 00:10:37.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The person
everyone is looking at</b></Default>

00:10:37.950 --> 00:10:39.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>isn't the real Ikumi Akagi.</b></Default>

00:10:41.370 --> 00:10:43.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it doesn't matter
that I'm a substitute</b></Default>

00:10:43.909 --> 00:10:45.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then what am I?</b></Default>

00:10:45.500 --> 00:10:47.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what I've been wondering.</b></Default>

00:10:47.409 --> 00:10:50.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At this point</b></Default>

00:10:51.120 --> 00:10:52.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't get it at all.</b></Default>

00:10:53.330 --> 00:10:55.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Akagi I know
is a greedy person</b></Default>

00:10:55.500 --> 00:10:58.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that always takes on everything
all by herself.</b></Default>

00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:01.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's so serious</b></Default>

00:11:01.500 --> 00:11:03.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And she looks good
in a nurse cosplay too.</b></Default>

00:11:04.539 --> 00:11:06.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's Akagi.</b></Default>

00:11:10.080 --> 00:11:11.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's with the head?</b></Default>

00:11:15.330 --> 00:11:18.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We walked together like this
on that day too.</b></Default>

00:11:18.159 --> 00:11:19.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We did.</b></Default>

00:11:19.370 --> 00:11:21.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you remember
what we talked about?</b></Default>

00:11:21.830 --> 00:11:24.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] What made you decide
on this high school</b></Default>

00:11:24.539 --> 00:11:25.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of all places?</b></Default>

00:11:25.700 --> 00:11:27.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought you'd have
gotten accepted</b></Default>

00:11:27.700 --> 00:11:29.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into a more prestigious school.</b></Default>

00:11:33.039 --> 00:11:34.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Azusagawa...
-Hmm?</b></Default>

00:11:37.120 --> 00:11:39.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Um, never mind. Just forget it.</b></Default>

00:11:43.159 --> 00:11:46.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Those words you were
trying to say back then</b></Default>

00:11:46.080 --> 00:11:48.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>did you say them
to my other self?</b></Default>

00:11:48.120 --> 00:11:50.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I had told you
all of my feelings</b></Default>

00:11:50.580 --> 00:11:52.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what would you
have done about it?</b></Default>

00:11:52.370 --> 00:11:54.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, for starters</b></Default>

00:11:55.159 --> 00:11:57.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even though you have
such a wonderful girlfriend?</b></Default>

00:11:57.700 --> 00:12:00.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not exactly
a popular person</b></Default>

00:12:00.080 --> 00:12:02.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'll take
all the love I can get.</b></Default>

00:12:02.159 --> 00:12:03.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, Azusagawa</b></Default>

00:12:03.950 --> 00:12:06.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you never give straightforward
answers to questions.</b></Default>

00:12:07.080 --> 00:12:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Neither do you.</b></Default>

00:12:17.789 --> 00:12:19.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crossing alarm ringing]</b></Default>

00:12:22.620 --> 00:12:23.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:12:25.159 --> 00:12:26.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's time to say goodbye.</b></Default>

00:12:28.289 --> 00:12:29.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you okay now?</b></Default>

00:12:30.250 --> 00:12:32.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It seems like
everything's set up now.</b></Default>

00:12:32.409 --> 00:12:34.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Huh?
-This is a message</b></Default>

00:12:34.120 --> 00:12:36.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from my other self, for you.</b></Default>

00:12:39.080 --> 00:12:41.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'M WAITING FOR YOU
AT THE REUNION</b></Default>

00:12:41.870 --> 00:12:42.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:12:43.250 --> 00:12:44.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you see it?</b></Default>

00:12:44.330 --> 00:12:46.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait! What is Akagi up to?</b></Default>

00:12:46.620 --> 00:12:48.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[train approaching]</b></Default>

00:12:48.909 --> 00:12:50.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Bye-bye.</b></Default>

00:13:04.870 --> 00:13:06.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait a sec! Uh...</b></Default>

00:13:07.200 --> 00:13:08.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:13:12.409 --> 00:13:15.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not too late.
I can still make the reunion.</b></Default>

00:13:15.370 --> 00:13:17.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:20.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:13:23.450 --> 00:13:25.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>ALL SEATS ARE RESERVED TODAY
FOR A REUNION</b></Default>

00:13:25.659 --> 00:13:27.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:13:28.080 --> 00:13:29.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all giggling]</b></Default>

00:13:29.250 --> 00:13:30.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That one time. Right?</b></Default>

00:13:30.539 --> 00:13:32.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Sakuta panting]</b></Default>

00:13:33.450 --> 00:13:35.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

00:13:41.409 --> 00:13:43.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why am I always
in these situations?</b></Default>

00:13:52.450 --> 00:13:53.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, that guy.</b></Default>

00:13:54.830 --> 00:13:55.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ugh.</b></Default>

00:13:55.870 --> 00:13:57.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAN 1] That's Azusagawa, right?</b></Default>

00:13:57.870 --> 00:14:00.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[MAN 2] Why?
-[MAN 3] Who invited him.</b></Default>

00:14:00.200 --> 00:14:01.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAN 4] Like I know.</b></Default>

00:14:05.200 --> 00:14:06.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Akagi.</b></Default>

00:14:07.539 --> 00:14:08.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all gasp]</b></Default>

00:14:08.870 --> 00:14:10.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[hushed whispers]</b></Default>

00:14:10.200 --> 00:14:11.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WOMAN 1] Ikumi was here?</b></Default>

00:14:11.580 --> 00:14:13.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[WOMAN 2] No way.
-[MAN] Since when?</b></Default>

00:14:15.000 --> 00:14:16.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've been here the whole time.</b></Default>

00:14:16.950 --> 00:14:19.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I got here about an hour ago.</b></Default>

00:14:19.659 --> 00:14:21.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was here
when Fujino came in late</b></Default>

00:14:21.870 --> 00:14:24.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and wanted to give a toast
to everybody.</b></Default>

00:14:24.289 --> 00:14:27.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When Tanimura tipped over
and broke a glass.</b></Default>

00:14:27.159 --> 00:14:30.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And even when Nakai
confessed his love to Ayusawa.</b></Default>

00:14:30.950 --> 00:14:33.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was right here the whole time.</b></Default>

00:14:37.950 --> 00:14:40.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Been a while, Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:14:41.450 --> 00:14:43.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you finally remember me?</b></Default>

00:14:43.580 --> 00:14:45.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had forgotten.</b></Default>

00:14:46.000 --> 00:14:47.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a bit harsh.</b></Default>

00:14:49.539 --> 00:14:50.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cutlery clinks]</b></Default>

00:14:52.620 --> 00:14:54.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You all saw that, right?</b></Default>

00:14:54.330 --> 00:14:57.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was inflicted
with puberty syndrome too.</b></Default>

00:14:57.159 --> 00:14:58.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold it right there, Akagi.</b></Default>

00:14:58.750 --> 00:15:00.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's nothing to joke about.</b></Default>

00:15:00.450 --> 00:15:02.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] If you think
it's a magic trick</b></Default>

00:15:02.580 --> 00:15:05.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>would someone be willing
to explain how I pulled it off?</b></Default>

00:15:06.409 --> 00:15:09.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The truth is</b></Default>

00:15:09.250 --> 00:15:11.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't deny it.</b></Default>

00:15:11.080 --> 00:15:13.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa wasn't mistaken
back then</b></Default>

00:15:13.870 --> 00:15:15.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but all of us were.</b></Default>

00:15:16.950 --> 00:15:19.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would you just drop this
already, Ikumi?</b></Default>

00:15:19.250 --> 00:15:22.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This puberty syndrome nonsense</b></Default>

00:15:22.450 --> 00:15:25.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My parents never let me
hear the end of that mess!</b></Default>

00:15:25.200 --> 00:15:28.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In high school, everyone kept
asking about middle school.</b></Default>

00:15:28.159 --> 00:15:30.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was as if
I was some criminal!</b></Default>

00:15:30.200 --> 00:15:33.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was even nervous about
coming here today, you know.</b></Default>

00:15:33.080 --> 00:15:34.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I was glad I came.</b></Default>

00:15:34.700 --> 00:15:36.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As I chatted with everyone here</b></Default>

00:15:36.580 --> 00:15:39.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I remembered that there were
fun times back then too.</b></Default>

00:15:40.000 --> 00:15:42.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So don't come and ruin
all of that again</b></Default>

00:15:42.250 --> 00:15:44.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with that ridiculous
puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:15:44.250 --> 00:15:46.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-of all things!
-That's right, Ikumi.</b></Default>

00:15:46.250 --> 00:15:47.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you after?</b></Default>

00:15:48.330 --> 00:15:51.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rina, why'd you come
if you were so nervous?</b></Default>

00:15:51.500 --> 00:15:52.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh...</b></Default>

00:15:52.539 --> 00:15:55.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] If you all felt uneasy</b></Default>

00:15:56.659 --> 00:15:59.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"I had a dream about
the school reunion today."</b></Default>

00:15:59.700 --> 00:16:01.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what you wrote, Rina.</b></Default>

00:16:01.700 --> 00:16:04.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here you are</b></Default>

00:16:04.250 --> 00:16:06.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>yet you believe
in the Dreaming tag.</b></Default>

00:16:08.000 --> 00:16:09.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You all too.</b></Default>

00:16:09.409 --> 00:16:11.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Back then</b></Default>

00:16:11.870 --> 00:16:14.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Azusagawa has lost it."</b></Default>

00:16:14.620 --> 00:16:17.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But clearly, we're the ones
that actually lost it.</b></Default>

00:16:18.200 --> 00:16:20.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We made fun of Azusagawa
with our ignorance.</b></Default>

00:16:21.289 --> 00:16:22.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We hurt him.</b></Default>

00:16:22.870 --> 00:16:25.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We labeled him as someone
who had gone insane</b></Default>

00:16:25.700 --> 00:16:28.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and we ruined his life
as he knew it.</b></Default>

00:16:29.409 --> 00:16:31.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, after knowing
we were wrong</b></Default>

00:16:31.539 --> 00:16:32.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we keep laughing it off</b></Default>

00:16:32.870 --> 00:16:35.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>without any intention
of making amends.</b></Default>

00:16:35.120 --> 00:16:36.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's insanity.</b></Default>

00:16:36.580 --> 00:16:38.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure, it's easy for you
to say that</b></Default>

00:16:38.539 --> 00:16:40.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it's way too late
for that now.</b></Default>

00:16:41.159 --> 00:16:42.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just like Rina said</b></Default>

00:16:43.039 --> 00:16:44.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because of that incident</b></Default>

00:16:44.450 --> 00:16:46.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>nothing went well
in my life either.</b></Default>

00:16:47.000 --> 00:16:50.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I got to high school</b></Default>

00:16:50.830 --> 00:16:53.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had a tough time every day</b></Default>

00:16:53.080 --> 00:16:54.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and it stuck with me.</b></Default>

00:16:54.750 --> 00:16:56.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then why are you...</b></Default>

00:16:56.370 --> 00:16:57.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if that's all true</b></Default>

00:16:58.039 --> 00:17:00.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the only one who has the right
to say it's too late</b></Default>

00:17:00.789 --> 00:17:02.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-is Azusagawa.
-[gasps]</b></Default>

00:17:12.200 --> 00:17:13.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just kidding!</b></Default>

00:17:14.039 --> 00:17:16.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, that went
really well, huh, Akagi?</b></Default>

00:17:16.910 --> 00:17:19.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Akagi and I
go to the same university.</b></Default>

00:17:19.329 --> 00:17:21.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I heard you guys
were having a reunion</b></Default>

00:17:21.410 --> 00:17:22.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I had her help me out.</b></Default>

00:17:22.829 --> 00:17:25.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Wait. No. It's--
-impressive magic trick. Huh?</b></Default>

00:17:25.789 --> 00:17:28.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Akagi's acting
was true to life, too.</b></Default>

00:17:28.450 --> 00:17:30.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This was all a big prank.</b></Default>

00:17:30.410 --> 00:17:32.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, it is too late
for all that stuff</b></Default>

00:17:32.619 --> 00:17:34.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that went down in middle school</b></Default>

00:17:34.579 --> 00:17:37.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and my life wasn't a complete
wash either, you know.</b></Default>

00:17:37.500 --> 00:17:38.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I'm being honest</b></Default>

00:17:38.700 --> 00:17:40.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I ended up
a whole lot happier</b></Default>

00:17:40.700 --> 00:17:42.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than the rest of you guys.</b></Default>

00:17:42.410 --> 00:17:44.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure you know this by now</b></Default>

00:17:44.329 --> 00:17:47.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I happen to be going out
with the famous Mai Sakurajima.</b></Default>

00:17:47.700 --> 00:17:49.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm just saying</b></Default>

00:17:50.039 --> 00:17:51.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for picking on me.</b></Default>

00:17:55.200 --> 00:17:58.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was where you're all
supposed to start laughing.</b></Default>

00:17:58.450 --> 00:18:00.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyway, that's what
I came to tell you all.</b></Default>

00:18:01.000 --> 00:18:02.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have a nice life.</b></Default>

00:18:02.500 --> 00:18:03.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See ya.</b></Default>

00:18:05.619 --> 00:18:06.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door closes]</b></Default>

00:18:16.250 --> 00:18:17.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:18:18.950 --> 00:18:20.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:18:35.119 --> 00:18:37.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Were you satisfied with that?</b></Default>

00:18:37.410 --> 00:18:38.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] Satisfied?</b></Default>

00:18:39.160 --> 00:18:42.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everything went perfectly
according to plan, right?</b></Default>

00:18:42.079 --> 00:18:44.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What plan are you talking about?</b></Default>

00:18:44.289 --> 00:18:45.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your master plan to gather</b></Default>

00:18:45.829 --> 00:18:47.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all our middle school
classmates</b></Default>

00:18:47.539 --> 00:18:49.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and force them
to acknowledge the existence</b></Default>

00:18:49.829 --> 00:18:51.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of puberty syndrome
in front of me.</b></Default>

00:18:52.789 --> 00:18:55.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why you planned
the reunion, wasn't it?</b></Default>

00:18:56.329 --> 00:18:59.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then, you lured me out
using the Dreaming tag</b></Default>

00:18:59.660 --> 00:19:02.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a massive lie
about you injuring someone.</b></Default>

00:19:03.950 --> 00:19:06.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess
the cat's out of the bag.</b></Default>

00:19:06.619 --> 00:19:09.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How long have you been
planning for today's events?</b></Default>

00:19:09.750 --> 00:19:12.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With the sudden onset
of puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:19:12.750 --> 00:19:15.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought that this was
the right thing to do.</b></Default>

00:19:15.369 --> 00:19:19.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After I found you during
the matriculation ceremony</b></Default>

00:19:19.950 --> 00:19:21.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was shocked.</b></Default>

00:19:21.789 --> 00:19:25.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa, you stood there
as if nothing happened.</b></Default>

00:19:25.329 --> 00:19:27.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were laughing
like you forgot</b></Default>

00:19:27.160 --> 00:19:29.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all about the painful memories
from the past.</b></Default>

00:19:30.000 --> 00:19:32.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And the fact that
I held on to that pain</b></Default>

00:19:32.500 --> 00:19:35.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>unable to become something</b></Default>

00:19:36.000 --> 00:19:39.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I felt so bad
I couldn't show my face.</b></Default>

00:19:39.660 --> 00:19:41.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>It's clear that</i>
<i>you've already moved on</b></Default>

00:19:42.000 --> 00:19:44.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>but I haven't made</i>
<i>any progress whatsoever.</i></b></Default>

00:19:45.160 --> 00:19:47.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>Those thoughts ate me alive</b></Default>

00:19:47.329 --> 00:19:49.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>and I just needed</i>
<i>to get away from there.</i></b></Default>

00:19:49.539 --> 00:19:50.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>It didn't matter where.</i></b></Default>

00:19:50.869 --> 00:19:52.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I just had to.</i></b></Default>

00:19:52.410 --> 00:19:54.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[man singing]</b></Default>

00:19:54.119 --> 00:19:55.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[soft gasp]</b></Default>

00:19:59.910 --> 00:20:02.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] You sure got away
to a very far place.</b></Default>

00:20:02.660 --> 00:20:06.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That being said, I thought I was
in a strange dream at first.</b></Default>

00:20:07.789 --> 00:20:11.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I assumed after spending a day</i>
<i>over in that other world</b></Default>

00:20:11.250 --> 00:20:14.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>I would be back here</i>
<i>when the next morning came.</i></b></Default>

00:20:15.160 --> 00:20:17.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>But I was still over there</b></Default>

00:20:18.119 --> 00:20:21.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b><i>so I had to believe</i>
<i>that everything was real.</i></b></Default>

00:20:21.750 --> 00:20:23.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] You never wanted
to come back?</b></Default>

00:20:24.289 --> 00:20:25.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] I did feel uneasy</b></Default>

00:20:26.039 --> 00:20:27.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but after about a month</b></Default>

00:20:27.869 --> 00:20:31.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I started thinking it was okay
for everything to stay that way.</b></Default>

00:20:31.579 --> 00:20:35.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] So I guess that world
was comfortable for you, huh?</b></Default>

00:20:35.119 --> 00:20:36.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] More than this one.</b></Default>

00:20:37.200 --> 00:20:38.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But in that world</b></Default>

00:20:38.660 --> 00:20:39.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you see</b></Default>

00:20:39.869 --> 00:20:43.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I failed college entrance exams</b></Default>

00:20:43.410 --> 00:20:44.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, and that way</b></Default>

00:20:44.539 --> 00:20:46.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you wouldn't have had
to see me at university.</b></Default>

00:20:47.039 --> 00:20:49.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>More than anything</b></Default>

00:20:49.079 --> 00:20:51.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that everything that happened
in middle school</b></Default>

00:20:51.500 --> 00:20:52.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>had finally been resolved.</b></Default>

00:20:52.950 --> 00:20:55.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I heard I resolved
the bit about my sister</b></Default>

00:20:55.660 --> 00:20:57.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by taking over
the broadcast room.</b></Default>

00:20:57.450 --> 00:20:58.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] That's right.</b></Default>

00:20:58.700 --> 00:21:01.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought I'd restart
everything over there.</b></Default>

00:21:01.119 --> 00:21:03.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought I could become
the person I wanted to be</b></Default>

00:21:03.829 --> 00:21:04.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in that world.</b></Default>

00:21:04.869 --> 00:21:07.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] You're saying the same
thing the other Akagi said.</b></Default>

00:21:09.039 --> 00:21:10.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Azusagawa?</b></Default>

00:21:10.910 --> 00:21:12.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:21:12.119 --> 00:21:14.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How can I let go
of my hateful self</b></Default>

00:21:14.450 --> 00:21:16.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that wasn't capable
of doing anything?</b></Default>

00:21:17.579 --> 00:21:19.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, it's simple.</b></Default>

00:21:19.910 --> 00:21:20.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really?</b></Default>

00:21:20.950 --> 00:21:23.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You just gotta
eat breakfast every day</b></Default>

00:21:23.410 --> 00:21:25.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>go to school</b></Default>

00:21:25.579 --> 00:21:28.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and have lots of trivial chats
with friends.</b></Default>

00:21:28.250 --> 00:21:30.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Go to work, take a bath</b></Default>

00:21:30.329 --> 00:21:32.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>brush your teeth</b></Default>

00:21:32.500 --> 00:21:34.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Although, you will
occasionally remember</b></Default>

00:21:34.619 --> 00:21:36.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>some of the bad things too.</b></Default>

00:21:36.579 --> 00:21:39.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When you do, you writhe around
in your bed for a bit</b></Default>

00:21:40.000 --> 00:21:41.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and then the next thing
you know</b></Default>

00:21:42.119 --> 00:21:44.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your alarm clock's waking you up
with a headache.</b></Default>

00:21:44.750 --> 00:21:46.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you eat breakfast
and head to school</b></Default>

00:21:46.950 --> 00:21:48.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to do it all over again.</b></Default>

00:21:48.950 --> 00:21:50.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How long do I need
to keep doing that?</b></Default>

00:21:51.039 --> 00:21:53.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hell if I know</b></Default>

00:21:53.079 --> 00:21:54.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Of course.</b></Default>

00:21:55.160 --> 00:21:58.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm so uncool</b></Default>

00:21:58.700 --> 00:22:00.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good thing
you figured that out today</b></Default>

00:22:01.869 --> 00:22:03.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>not tomorrow</b></Default>

00:22:03.119 --> 00:22:05.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the day after, a week later</b></Default>

00:22:05.079 --> 00:22:06.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or even a year from now.</b></Default>

00:22:07.200 --> 00:22:09.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though I took quite a detour
to get here.</b></Default>

00:22:11.250 --> 00:22:13.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm glad it was today.</b></Default>

00:22:13.910 --> 00:22:15.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, right?</b></Default>

00:22:15.079 --> 00:22:17.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ closing theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:22:18.119 --> 00:22:20.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] You know</b></Default>

00:22:20.579 --> 00:22:22.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when you gloated
about dating Mai.</b></Default>

00:22:22.750 --> 00:22:24.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I heard reunions
are for bragging</b></Default>

00:22:24.539 --> 00:22:26.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about how much better you are.</b></Default>

00:22:26.289 --> 00:22:28.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] But that was
really spiteful.</b></Default>

00:22:28.329 --> 00:22:30.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll definitely
be giving Mai my thanks.</b></Default>

00:22:31.039 --> 00:22:33.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was protecting me
the whole time today, too.</b></Default>

00:22:38.950 --> 00:22:40.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SPECIAL INTERVIEW
MAI SAKURAJIMA</b></Default>

00:22:41.450 --> 00:22:43.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NOVEMBER 28TH</b></Default>

00:22:44.910 --> 00:22:46.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] You know, Mai?</b></Default>

00:22:46.369 --> 00:22:47.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Hmm?</b></Default>

00:22:47.410 --> 00:22:50.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's something I really need
to apologize to you about.</b></Default>

00:22:50.869 --> 00:22:52.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you cheat on me again?</b></Default>

00:22:52.329 --> 00:22:54.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When have I ever cheated on you?</b></Default>

00:22:54.289 --> 00:22:57.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're quick to make
acquaintances with other girls.</b></Default>

00:22:57.500 --> 00:23:00.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You see</b></Default>

00:23:00.289 --> 00:23:02.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I bragged about
dating Mai Sakurajima.</b></Default>

00:23:02.619 --> 00:23:04.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't really mind that.</b></Default>

00:23:04.410 --> 00:23:06.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, it's true, isn't it?</b></Default>

00:23:06.200 --> 00:23:08.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, yeah, it is, but--</b></Default>

00:23:08.450 --> 00:23:11.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or rather, could it be
that you're trying to say</b></Default>

00:23:11.200 --> 00:23:13.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not a girlfriend
you can brag about?</b></Default>

00:23:14.789 --> 00:23:16.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL] Do you have a moment?</b></Default>

00:23:16.329 --> 00:23:17.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BOTH] Hmm?</b></Default>

00:23:17.369 --> 00:23:19.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-No, I'm really busy.
-Of course.</b></Default>

00:23:20.369 --> 00:23:21.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] You must be Akagi.</b></Default>

00:23:21.910 --> 00:23:23.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, sit.</b></Default>

00:23:24.910 --> 00:23:27.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Should I give the two of you
some privacy?</b></Default>

00:23:27.160 --> 00:23:28.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No.</b></Default>

00:23:28.160 --> 00:23:30.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This actually
concerns you, Sakurajima.</b></Default>

00:23:30.910 --> 00:23:32.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It concerns me?</b></Default>

00:23:33.539 --> 00:23:34.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Take a look.</b></Default>

00:23:34.619 --> 00:23:36.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A MESSAGE
FROM AZUSAGAWA OVER HERE</b></Default>

00:23:36.619 --> 00:23:37.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>TO AZUSAGAWA OVER THERE</b></Default>

00:23:38.250 --> 00:23:39.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, is this--</b></Default>

00:23:39.369 --> 00:23:40.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] Please don't worry.</b></Default>

00:23:41.000 --> 00:23:44.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can assure you that I'm the me
who was born in this world.</b></Default>

00:23:44.250 --> 00:23:46.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay. And what's the message?</b></Default>

00:23:50.000 --> 00:23:52.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>FIND TOUKO KIRISHIMA
MAI-SAN IS IN DANGER!</b></Default>

00:23:52.579 --> 00:23:53.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both gasp]</b></Default>

00:23:56.000 --> 00:23:58.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] <i>Oh, Azusagawa.</i>
<i>You're such a rascal.</i></b></Default>

00:23:58.750 --> 00:24:00.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NEXT EPISODE
#8 SECRETS AND PROMISES</b></Default>
